{"tid":2135019,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發時空．沈旭暉 】 「DQ邏輯」與香港的未來","createTime":"2020-08-01T06:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T06:45:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2172630e62a8abe56ee11feaa8114333d4173d5c","tid":2135019,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"【突發時空．沈旭暉 013🇭🇰】<br />\n「DQ邏輯」與香港的未來<br />\nJul 31, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sj7GWc1EzII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsj7GWc1EzII&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PqEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=7e6350f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sj7GWc1EzII</a><br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n134K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n根據北京理解，香港特區政府自然要完全按照中央政府的意思去管治香港，向有監督權的兩辦匯報。而香港特區政府本身，也必須行政主導一切，任何屬於制度內的存在，都不能挑戰行政主導這原則，無論是立法機關、司法機關、公務員工會還是區議會，因為香港制度內毋需要任何制衡，一切都要回歸「民主集中制」基本點。以上這條真正的紅線，才是現在的DQ線。至於說出來的原因：甚麼支持國際制裁、原則上反對國安法、無條件否決財政預算案等，都是虛線。而北京對非建制陣營傳達的訊號，亦清晰不過。<br />\n<br />\n⏺ 文字版見Patreon:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/39890756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F39890756&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PqEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=7768db33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/39890756</a><br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PqEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=c0e3363b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PqEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=5b42d39a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nPatreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon